Tasks for topic Movable joints

Wheel of fun activities

Objective:

Undestand the work and process of joint movement with help of mini-fun activities


10 mini-fun activities:

1.Rotate your wrists in circles

2. Hop on one leg

3. Do 10 jumping jacks

4. Walk in place for 30 seconds

5. Rotate your shoulders forward and backward

6. Clap above your head 5 times

7. Try balancing on one foot for 10 seconds

8. Tilt your head left and right

9. Move your elbows in big circles

10. Sing a song in english and dance

Identify the 

Joint by movement

Objective:

Undestand how joints function through personal movement

Arm rotation

Raise your arm and rotate it.

Elbow bending

Bend and straighten your elbow.

Head tilting

Tilt your head side to side.
